text: Very convenient if staying in the Village hotel above. Not the biggest, but a good selection nonetheless.

Food quality is so bad. I just bought watermelon and chicken, both have gone bad!!! This is not the first time it happened. I threw away at least 5 watermelons that I bought from FP Katong V before. You need to check and improve on your storage on fresh food. This is not acceptable!
We stayed at the hotel in the same building, so this store was very convenient for us. It had everything we needed. Prices were good.

Oh wow this visit impressed us. Haven’t been back here in ages. The layout display is so eye candy. Much nicer display than all previous years.

Italy display, Japanese display, imports from all over the world.

Items were all neatly filled, sorted out, organized & visually pleasant. Kudos display team.
Has many things. Don’t have chopped Japanese leek. Sad. Thank you very much though. Clean and nice.
